 e-family retrofit. \n \nJoin TBDA\, Illinois Green Alliance\, and Sturm B
 uilders for a free\, mid-construction tour of a healthy\, low-energy sing
 le-family retrofit on March 31\, 2026\, at 12:30 pm. This home will be a 
 LEED certified project\, providing new comfortable interiors with great i
 ndoor air quality and a significantly improved building envelope. https:/
 /www.skokie.org/calendar.aspx?EID=4723
